## The Challenge

A mid-size logistics company was spending over 40 hours per week on manual data entry, invoice processing, and shipment tracking updates across three different systems.

## Our Solution

We built a custom automation platform that:

- **Integrates** all three systems via API connections
- **Automates** data entry and invoice processing
- **Tracks** shipments in real-time with automatic status updates
- **Alerts** the team when exceptions need human attention

## The Results

- **85%** reduction in manual processing time
- **99.7%** data accuracy (up from 94%)
- **40+ hours** saved per week
- **3 month** payback period

The team now focuses on exception handling and customer relationships instead of data entry.
